title: Ramiro Cazares Jr
text: These guys helped me find the right parts for my car. Now i have asked if the cold air intake will pass smog and they said yes but I will have to wait and see to make sure that it will. Besides that rough little patch great site. Recommend for any Civic owners and would like fast service.
